{
  "name": "RPlog_Commute_part_2",
  "title": "The Long Commute, Part 2",
  "summary": "Continuing their flight from Malign's tireless Sith battle droids in the Ord Vaxal jungle, the Padawan Enb'Zik and his Horansi wife Snarl debate scaling the bluffs versus going underground to reach the layered prison city of Old Soren. When orbital bombardment begins walking a precise line of fire toward the city, signaling that the droids have found their crashed ship, Zik senses the danger and they sprint for cover. Guided by the Force and Snarl's keen ears, Zik locates a ferrocrete storm-drain cover; the pair heave it aside, drop into the tunnel, and let it crash back into place above them. In the pitch dark, Enb'Zik reaches into the Living Force to make the disturbed soil overhead sprout into fast-grown vegetation, masking their escape from the converging droids before he lights a glowrod and the two press on through the drain toward the city.",
